h atau libur Lebaran bisa naik hingga 90 persen,\" kata Ketua Persatuan Hotel dan Restoran Bantul M Nur di Bantul, Kamis.</span><br [removed]: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21.84px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br [removed]: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21.84px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span [removed]: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21.84px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Menurut dia, tingkat hunian hotel berbintang di Bantul rata-rata per hari di atas 40 persen atau lebih tinggi dari rata-rata pondok wisata, namun saat liburan rata-rata tingkat hunian hampir sama.</span><br [removed]: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21.84px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br [removed]: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21.84px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span [removed]: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: no